<li>Avoid alcohol.</li>
<li>Do not take calcium, aluminum, magnesium or Iron supplements within 2 hours of taking this medication.</li>
<li>Increase dietary intake of magnesium, folate, vitamin B6, B12, and/or consider taking a multivitamin.</li>
<li>Take on empty stomach: 1 hour before or 2 hours after meals.</li>
<li>Take with a full glass of water.</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>